{"tid":1784867,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[開始羸] 傳陳國強、王雪紅有意悉售持股 退出TVB (11:19)","createTime":"2019-12-16T03:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T05:30:18.000Z","uid":164511,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b1212a9b001b07e2a56928e16f344f30793bb780","tid":1784867,"uid":164511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T03:38:32.000Z","msg":"電視廣播（TVB)(0511)股東內部不和，股東之一的「殼王」陳國強，以及台灣女首富王雪紅，有意悉售持股，待陳國強與另一大股東黎瑞剛取得共識後便成事，料於短期內公布，而陳國強亦最快於明年一月卸任董事局主席一職。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，陳國強2011年與王雪紅入主TVB，而黎瑞剛於2015年亦加入，但雙方對公司發展方向有分歧，「使陳國強無心戀戰，加上前年遇空難大難不死的經歷，陳國強去意亦愈來愈濃」，並有消息指其於董事會上不止一次稱要退休。<br />\n<br />\n由於陳王二人的股權擁有大多數表決權，故陳國強退出，就必須找一個合資格的香港人做持牌人。另外，報道又引述消息指，高層換班陸續有來。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完全係步入左亞視收皮之前幾年既mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627a8ca35b209f13cbf1deb5b98beed20aa49fa2","tid":1784867,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T03:41:18.000Z","msg":"【第十柒期牆紙】起來，不願做奴隸的人們<br />\nTG <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hkBSGL744lGwoqCHTcH8MN0%3D&h=c79b9d83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\nFB <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F852wallpaper%2F&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hkBSGL744lGwoqCHTcH8MN0%3D&h=03e99efc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1778521/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1778521/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o471rTe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo471rTe.jpg&h=846ba8e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77e9e6f8a1f6f5971d29374efb3c9da02ef983ec","tid":1784867,"uid":289191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T03:42:11.000Z","